{"title":"Síndrome hematofagocitico-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Síndrome hematofagocitico-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Sindrome de Activacion Macrofágica (MAS) / Síndrome Hemofagocítico /\\NLinfohistiocitosis Hemofagocítica (HLH)","guid":"lI9q8CnbbqV0UQc_S2sg3Q","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Caso Clínico","guid":"Bqy6gWwnJtVmPUCoYflMZQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Información\\Nde paciente","guid":"SUjHHxvQ5uITGFHSuWw7vQ","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"- Edad: 35 años","guid":"DkZeNiFVLvUNfYBuEFkrbw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"- Sexo: Femenino","guid":"Vh4kSUecOoxqXZLbPv4VKA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"- Antecedentes: Diagnóstico de enfermedad de Still del adulto\\Nhace 2 años, en tratamiento con metotrexato y corticoides.","guid":"bohxVy_Y4Th0PmR1GLy3TA","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Motivo de\\Nconsulta","guid":"D0RK11csAKzPd0FBwObcdw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- Fiebre persistente de 39.5°C por 1 semana, a pesar del tratamiento habitual","guid":"TdnHSXSTyk8VY34IBPJKeA","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"- Empeoramiento de síntomas articulares y aparición de exantema cutáneo","guid":"d6Ryuwd5g9IkBJWgayZsJQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"- Dolor abdominal y vómitos en los últimos 3 días","guid":"fM7DlUar6rR-vaeKc2vxgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Examen físico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- Temperatura: 40°C","guid":"RoFBDThXFXYX_SMATS37jg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"- Frecuencia cardíaca: 120 lpm","guid":"JH48S346Y6kvJ0fzMsSagQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"- Presión arterial: 90/60 mmHg","guid":"H4-SnjykyGFDHcXwda225w","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"- Exantema maculopapular en tronco, cuello y extremidades","guid":"BEEC7S17WMs0q8wPcsl0RA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"- Artritis en muñecas, codos, rodillas y tobillos","guid":"XVQ6AyjqMIQLhiuQKy4BTA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"- Hepatoesplenomegalia dolorosa","guid":"HX361CDpqZgwIEvFFSJtjw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"- Linfadenopatías cervicales y axilares","guid":"KGMta1Qk4WUASNm0JTHxAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"- Hemoglobina: 7.8 g/dL","guid":"GtDMGn8GgT4YneKDYVINJw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"- Leucocitos: 2,000/mm³ (neutrófilos: 55%, linfocitos: 35%)","guid":"N12WtDCbBYQugAi1W9vTAA","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"- Plaquetas: 60,000/mm³","guid":"LtVpLV2nUKgOoG2BTmT7yw","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"- AST: 580 U/L, ALT: 420 U/L","guid":"GkwZClG-M3JEErKyHo0b9w","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"- Ferritina: 35,000 ng/mL","guid":"fzmMPXi-fsERVpA8XI3GQQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"18","text":"- Triglicéridos: 400 mg/dL","guid":"IaivRhzcu8wHu8eNPyaqGg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"18","text":"- Fibrinógeno: 90 mg/dL","guid":"PcZlZTfcE1JUSRepZimS0A","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"18","text":"- Receptor IL-2 soluble (CD25): 3,500 U/mL","guid":"DAD0uFSR8V0LW4PQJtHA0g","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"18","text":"- Estudio de médula ósea: Hemofagocitosis presente","guid":"U5hymyP5ZlMII835CvYJUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"- Síndrome de activación macrofágica secundario a enfermedad de Still del adulto","guid":"VJRr1zaj1q5m0dxQA2nVBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"1","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"- Pulsos de metilprednisolona (1 g/día por 5 días), seguido de prednisona 1 mg/kg/día","guid":"FEsnVnVySdFRztDPLpdAYA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"- Ciclosporina A (3-5 mg/kg/día)","guid":"RzB9QxXhg4FNJFxYRmoJgQ","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"- Antibióticos de amplio espectro (meropenem y vancomicina)","guid":"DqACQ1567JQi98_CMEixiQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"- Soporte transfusional con glóbulos rojos y plaquetas","guid":"e1eoYCqzl09vb1ujOR4NxQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"30","text":"- Monitoreo estrecho en unidad de cuidados intensivos","guid":"Yo-qokO4c0wfR6CVbpCfWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"1","text":"Seguimiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"- Mejoría clínica gradual tras inicio de tratamiento inmunosupresor","guid":"GEpkqSqjJGUVYmAsa-LXRA","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"- Resolución de fiebre y citopenias después de 2 semanas","guid":"TpyKuR2GLiV22OCUIzD2kA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"- Disminución progresiva de ferritina y normalización de perfil hepático","guid":"VCoE012qvOQmmsuVaHUsKQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"- Ajuste de dosis de ciclosporina A según niveles séricos","guid":"Ux0GtnhpnGQXDGyKGk2D-Q","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"- Alta hospitalaria tras 4 semanas, con plan de seguimiento ambulatorio por reumatología","guid":"Dksf5mQwyOJgt416HOsiKQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"36","text":"- Consideración de terapia biológica (anakinra o tocilizumab) en caso de refractariedad o recaída","guid":"Qqu1dgOvXTxNM9OyPgNd1g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"Definición ","guid":"yDs3rJQmnFjLZpkrxgkTng","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Raro síndrome híperinflamatório","guid":"lOso_ozkMuKGa5-OiBTFIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Perlas","guid":"bo8zrHclC7ZjgGFLL4guYQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"¿Qué sistema está involucrado principalmente en la fisiopatología de HLH? R: El sistema inmune innato y adaptativo. (1,2)","guid":"H40eGXlghBlC0D4tIhTYUw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"¿Cuáles son las citopenias más frecuentes en HLH? R: Anemia y trombocitopenia. (1,2)","guid":"Kmfq0lc1KfYsnbryD_k8Wg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"¿Cuál es el examen de laboratorio característico en HLH? R: Hiperferritinemia. (1,2)","guid":"EddOAHxkh8Q7nuM0XCJEGQ","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"¿Cuáles son los dos tipos principales de HLH? R: Primaria (genética) y secundaria (reactiva). (1,2)","guid":"PuOj9ncQ69Q98XO1NNZVhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"WVvN7hALjpUu4vVqKeeY2A","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Raro síndrome hiperinflamatorio (1)","guid":"ApibXTM1QHAuiju4Q1uw6g","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Caracterizado por\\Nactivación inmune intensa","guid":"LAOFA7VaS7f798m0LBx_Yg","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Fiebre","guid":"OhBJz3tCk37zVDQ1Ey8NTw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Citopenias","guid":"l9fWJ7rk8HNs8sopFKqFTA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"Hepatoesplenomegalia","guid":"Cot0GVRqQ6rK1KCNMp7hnw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"Hiperferritinemia","guid":"WCBj9XdmddDRF0xLGibJsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"Fisiopatológicamente ocurre una desregulación inmune adquirida o congénita que compromete la vía citotóxica de NK y CTL. (1)","guid":"BU4PN0Ak_8o8ZjX6c91C4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"N0oLgB_ml0UjZXFEVtcpmQ","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Desregulación de la vía citotóxica de NK y CTL lleva a hipercitokinemia y activación de linfocitos y macrófagos en tejidos periféricos. (1,2)","guid":"GUcbXmY1r3F47AHsQ68GMQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Disfunción de NK y CTL por defectos genéticos (HLH 1ria) o gatillada por infecciones, malignidad, AI, etc. (HLH 2ria). (2)","guid":"PWrZZyWJvN9TqEKLT0InZw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Macrófagos activados secretan IL-1, IL-6, IL-18, TNFα → Hiperinflamación. (2)","guid":"Ie5Eow9HJcArZGuBYNHomg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"Objetivos terapéuticos: Interrumpir ciclo de hiperinflamación inhibiendo proliferación/activación de células T. (1)","guid":"BlgRlGlV3zYVqD4gX7Pfgw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"Potenciales blancos: Citoquinas proinflamatorias (IL-1, IL-6, TNFα, IFNγ), JAK/STAT. (2)","guid":"eWFty0SLM4oJm3hbe_oJKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"d8Bz-jgltBQ_VboTfQ6DMg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"HLH 1ria es rara en adultos. HLH 2ria es más frecuente. (1)","guid":"eEqz3nu78A1w68YVL5S_Xg","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Alta morbilidad y mortalidad (20-50% y hasta 70% en algunos tipos). (2)","guid":"G6KHUhRRN1oGa-j4NOmisA","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"eobmy39X6uR4mKjhN_HAMw","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Inmunodeficiencias primarias (HLH 1ria). (1,2)","guid":"JOGnw0xA620HM-eaRs_sZw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Infecciones (VEB, CMV, leishmaniasis, etc), malignidad\\N(linfoma), enf. autoinmunes (LES, enf. Still), drogas. (1,2)","guid":"W4gRLTKYUxsnodUBYeAiwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"Causas","guid":"G-4yUj1KEyFBlAJEFU-gHQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Clasificación ","guid":"843WZyOQiGLbmutD78WYgw","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Primario\\N(Genético)","guid":"xDCmxvSPV7voD0faM-1b2w","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Raro en adultos ","guid":"UeR_ydHoxouR2pnLZ0qPAw","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Síndromes genéticos ","guid":"mRwGSgAvX98bevz5H-zoIA","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"X-linked lymphoproliferative disorder","guid":"22tekOJ2h9_XkC1pE_dIqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Generalmente gatillado por infecciones","guid":"f3F0jfiw3kQnyrFMU5jbRw","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"71","text":"Secundario\\N(Reactivo)","guid":"OGUC1WoWlt7IFVezf6lgog","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Infección\\N50%","guid":"VG-3wDeyR3gnkoh2qeTmSg","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Especialmente virales\\NVEB","guid":"Md7vNjOBdjTQEagRKPXWNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"Malignidad","guid":"_G35ECWWs1cOGmDv_hbhrg","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Hematológicas \\NLinfoma","guid":"zGA6wcYRo4sF0WR2Mgs7Mg","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"Medicamentos","guid":"4TLX_KZyrWqCrGLHC4fDaQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Inhibidores de checkpoint inmunes","guid":"ma8042uMX0NduZ2aY7zQeA","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"77","text":"Autoinmine \\NMacrophage-activation syndrome (MAS)","guid":"3pFZ75WN-Ipezeq4ufHMnQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Enfermedad de Still del adulto","guid":"QrK_772DzeRO51JVvZxOVQ","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"LES","guid":"XBom0wtzP-CmsdwAI8ffKA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"70","text":"Enfermedades reumatológicas","guid":"e-E7SDGgiugc531odmgiEw","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"1. Artritis Idiopática\\NJuvenil sistémica (AIJs):","guid":"MPh1zRWAJkouWeJGVdodkA","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"- Incidencia de MAS en AIJs: 10-20%. (1,2)","guid":"YcERtzWNyeEcqgn3PUki5A","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"- Principal enfermedad reumatológica pediátrica asociada a MAS. (1,2)","guid":"aCYc_ERL3vgfKUWlBBRPTg","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"- Mayor riesgo en AIJs con: Inicio <1 año, actividad persistente, uso de biológicos (IL-1, IL-6). (2)","guid":"AZXyGmC9R-oZY-9sA2s4xg","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"2. Enfermedad de Still\\Ndel adulto (AOSD):","guid":"K-zCiiqtmLJ9APNsL0HxPg","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"- Incidencia de MAS en AOSD: 10-25%. (1,2)","guid":"e0z8C3OlMUUq4dPQR6hPcQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","pare